Package: unifyr
Title: Post-Import Tools for Analysis-Ready Panel Data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Lavanya", "Desiraju", , "desirajulavanya@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides tidyverse-friendly tools for auditing, diagnosing, and
    documenting panel datasets after import. The package focuses on transparent
    panel structure checks, gap detection, duplicate identification, and
    reproducible audit trails for empirical research workflows.
